<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> tirumakaḷ polap perunilac celviyu n=ta ṉakke yurimai
<lb n="2"/>pūṇṭamai maṉakkoḷak kān=ta ḷurccālai kalamaṟuttaruḷi <unclear>veṅ</unclear>kaināṭu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṅ kaṅkapāṭiyu nuḷampapāṭit taṭikaipāṭiyuṅ kuṭamalaināṭuṅ ko
<lb n="4" break="no"/>llamuṅ kaliṅkamu meṇṭicai pukaḻtara Īḻamaṇṭalamu n=ti ṇṭiṟal veṉṟi taṇṭāṟkoṇ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭu taṉṉeḻil vaḷar Ūḻiyu ḷellā yāṇṭu n=to ḻutaka viḷaṅkum yāṇṭey ceḻiya
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rai tecukoḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>kecari<hi rend="grantha">panma</hi> rāṉa <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">jade</hi> vaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="21">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 1</num>āvatu <unclear>tiru</unclear>
<lb n="7" break="no"/>muṉaippāṭi m<unclear>e</unclear>lūrnāṭṭut tevatāṉa n=ti runāvalūrt tiruttoṇṭi<hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> ramuṭaiya m(ā)h<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice>tevaṟku mummaṭicoḻa <hi rend="grantha">brahma</hi> mārā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>yar ka<hi rend="grantha">nmi</hi> kaḻumparuṭaiyāṉ cittirakuttaṉ Aiyyakku<unclear>maraṭi</unclear> Ivvūriṟ palavakaiyālu n=ta ṇṭaṅkoṇṭu tirunāvalūrkkallā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>l Iṭuvitta paṭṭam 1 niṟai Irupattoru kaḻañce Āṟu mañcāṭiyum In=ta <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>koyi lil Āṭiyaruḷukiṟa kūttarkku Iṭuvi
<lb n="10" break="no"/>tta pātapīṭam 1- ṉāṟ cen=ta karuvu n=ta rāvumāka nāvalūrk kolāl niṟai Āyirat teḻunūṟ ṟaiympatiṉ palamum Itu ca
<lb n="11" break="no"/>n=ti rātittavaṟ <hi rend="grantha">panmāheśvara rakṣai <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied></hi>
</p>

